data.description: Investor's Dream! Charming 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath Oasis on Expansive Lot!Welcome to your next investment opportunity! Nestled on a spacious, level lot enveloped by a complete fence, this single-level gem offers unparalleled potential for savvy investors. Situated minutes from the TN/GA stateline, this property boasts convenience and accessibility, appealing to renters and buyers alike. With two good sized bedrooms and a well-appointed bath, this home provides comfortable living spaces ideal for small families, young professionals, or retirees. The large, level, fenced lot offers endless possibilities for expansion, landscaping, or outdoor entertainment areas, making it an enticing feature for tenants or future buyers.Whether you're looking to flip, rent, or renovate, this property presents a prime canvas to maximize your returns and capitalize on the booming real estate market. With a single-level layout and manageable lot size, upkeep is a breeze, minimizing overhead costs and maximizing profitability.Don't miss out on this exceptional investment opportunity! Schedule a viewing today and unlock the potential of this hidden gem. Special financing is available for this property. The lender will provide a buydown of 1% for one year off current rates for the buyer. The lender will provide specific rates and APRs for your client's particular situation based on their personal qualifications. Ask your agent for more details on this offer today!
